net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components

Class ComponentManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.components.ComponentManagerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentManager

    public class ComponentManagerImpl
extends Object
implements ComponentManager
    This is a test implementation of the ComponentManager interface. Instead of real components only strings are created whose names represent the corresponding components. So the builder's results should be easy to test.
    Version:
    $Id: ComponentManagerImpl.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
